            <p>Since its inception in year 2016, our Department of General Surgery, is working with the motto of providing quality health care to workers and their families.</p>
            <p>With sate of the art general ward of 100 beds  , with 50 beds each for female and male patients at 3rd and 5th floors respectively, with 6 patients in each cubicle, and isolated beds for burns cases.</p>
            <p>Surgical ICU located in  2nd  floor for the critical patients . </p>
            <p>Postoperative ward in 3rd floor of  inpatient block.</p>
            <p>We work round the clock to provide best quality care to our patients. </p>
            <p>A department with 4 consultants, few SRs and JRs, working as 4 units, we cater to 250 - 300 outpatients/day,   (~ 4500-5000 patients per month)</p>
            <p>We Perform<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•	30-40 emergency surgeries per month,<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•	100-150 major surgeries per month which includes <br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Laparoscopic procedures,<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Thyroid and Breast  surgeries<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Major laparotomies<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Hernia surgeries (both conventional and minimal invasive)<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Stapler Haemorrhoidectomies &<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-Varicose veins  to name a few.<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•	100-150 minor surgeries a month.<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•	Endoscopies (upper and lower GI)<br>
            </p>
            <p>Besides clinical work, we are involved in research work and have published many papers, upgrade our skills through workshops and CMEs conducted at our institute and outside.</p>
            <p>We are also involved in training undergraduate students. </p>
            <p>We aim to develop this institute at par with the premiere institutes in our country.</p>
